    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that's basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
