      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, featuring the iconic 13B-REW rotary powerplant with its complex sequential twin-turbocharger setup intact and functioning flawlessly. This example boasts exceptional chassis rigidity and a near-perfect 50/50 weight distribution. Recent compression tests yield high, consistent results across all rotor faces. The drivetrain remains factory-spec, including the smooth-shifting 5-speed manual and Torsen limited-slip differential. Meticulously maintained with an emphasis on thermal management, the cooling system has been refreshed to preserve the integrity of the apex seals. A true collector\u2019s piece with original paint and a pristine interior.",
